caption.body: Austin-based filmmaker Kayla Abuda Galang offers instructional English translations for Tagalog conversational phrases and common expressions, while humorously communicating what it feels like to be sad and bored within the confines of your home.   See “Learning Tagalog with Kayla” by Kayla Abuda Galang (@nannerisms) in the Video Arts Gallery, located pre-security in the International Terminal with daily operating hours of 5:00am to 10:00pm, or online at: https://bit.ly/3yoWNSH
